{"tid":292034,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"港女港嬸話自己好易養🤔","createTime":"2017-06-21T04:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T08:08:38.000Z","uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b75f7975f852d69fb46b7148c10cd65dfc1c0858","tid":292034,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:38:55.000Z","msg":"今朝食早餐聽到港女親子丼嘅對話：<br />\n👵🏻🍝：我地都好易養姐，都唔明啲男人成日有咩好呻。<br />\n👩🏻💅🏻：咪係，我地一日三餐，有間樓住下有幾難！<br />\n👵🏻🍝：啲男人成日出去玩，晒埋啲無謂錢。<br />\n👩🏻💅🏻：啲錢留係屋企比我地用仲好啦！佢地亂咁使。<br />\n👵🏻🍝：我地咪用返係佢身上。<br />\n👩🏻💅🏻：我keep起啲錢都係為佢好咋！<br />\n👵🏻🍝：佢地用錢都係買埋啲無謂野，像飲飲食食。<br />\n👩🏻💅🏻：男人都係信唔過，不如自己啲近身錢穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n男士們，當係地不斷努力搵錢時，不要忘記你背後女人對人有多愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a881ec0dba67b8ae77092f5eec67c73743d3f8ec","tid":292034,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c092003d05387d6a870346ed88ae5c7bd0fb83","tid":292034,"uid":120123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:11:52.000Z","msg":"飲飲食食都無謂 ? 練仙 ?"},{"pid":"5529e0e29efae0fbda87bf2db613e2dedde25dec","tid":292034,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:14:21.000Z","msg":"港男上進啲，比心機搵錢啦"},{"pid":"72741a5283bcb3da4c8f400f2380b02ed893b523","tid":292034,"uid":72906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:15:57.000Z","msg":"買衫買鞋手袋唔係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705bc2610a4b995e5466b8649413bf0bd9b8d089","tid":292034,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"含吹奶啜做齊未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b24c7d208a7419662d1c435e7125d030e3ee5b","tid":292034,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"我都想知係屋企可以玩到咩？"},{"pid":"bb060035826d121